<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />God whom I praise, do not be silent,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />For the wicked and deceitful attack me;</para>

<para style="q1">they speak lies against me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />They surround me and say hateful things,</para>

<para style="q1">and they attack me without cause.</para>
